{"tid":482018,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有樓有居留權】中國富豪新寵：希臘房地產","createTime":"2017-11-27T17:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T08:41:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a18fb5f73adf71f601cef538027e1190fe7bfe21","tid":482018,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/118193826_900x675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F118193826_900x675.jpg&h=50425734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《日經中文網》報道，中國投資者正積極進入希臘的樓市，在購買希臘房地產的外國人當中，中國人佔了42.1%。居留權或許能夠解釋中國投資者的熱情。希臘自2013年推出「黃金簽證」計劃，只要在希臘購買房産或投資建築等25萬歐元以上，投資者及其家屬即可獲得5年的居留許可。<br />\n<br />\nSpitogatos<br />\nPhoto from Spitogatos<br />\n<br />\n該居留權以連續持有房地產為條件，可以進行更新。希臘是《申根公約》成員國，其居民毋須邊境審查即可自由出入歐盟大部份國家。因此，持有希臘居留權往返歐洲各國可謂十分方便。<br />\n<br />\nSpitogatos<br />\nPhoto from Spitogatos<br />\n<br />\n根據希臘政府統計，截至2017年9月已有2,014名外國人在該國購買房地產（當中有850名投資者是中國人），投資額和相關收入超過10億歐元。根據希臘房地產廣告網站Spitogatos的統計，過去1年訪問該網頁英文版的中國訪客急升3倍，該網頁近期將推出中文版。"},{"pid":"1c79649e04c1c00be9d54f47bbb47c78cb1b3c29","tid":482018,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:58:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2017/11/21/article/44190/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2Farticle%2F44190%2F&d=Dm165pHbRYEt%2BfaYXMEeUqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=07a86d7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2017/11/21/article/44190/</a>"},{"pid":"822d1d81ead893905a536e05faa051e76b95e031","tid":482018,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T22:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd595d8f2d731cb267aee722d0ad7d2ef